Package com.amazonaws.kinesisvideo.parser.ebml

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EBMLParserCallbacks
    The EBMLParser invokes these callbacks when it detects the start, end and contents of elements.
    EBMLParserCallbacks.ElementPathSupplier  
    EBMLTypeInfoProvider
    An interface that vends type information used by the EBML parser.
    ParserBulkByteSource
    An interface representing a byte source for the parser which allows bulk reads.
    ParserByteSource
    Represents a source of bytes that can be parsed by the EBML parser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EBMLElementMetaData
    Class that represents the metadata of a single EBML element in an EBML stream.
    EBMLElementMetaData.EBMLElementMetaDataBuilder  
    EBMLParser
    This class is used to parse a stream of EBML.
    EBMLTypeInfo
    The type information for an EBML element.
    EBMLTypeInfo.EBMLTypeInfoBuilder  
    EBMLUtils
    Class used to parse EBML Ids and Sizes that make up the EBML element's meta data.
    InputStreamParserByteSource
    An implementation of ParserByteSource that wraps an input stream containing the EBML stream.
    MkvTypeInfos
    Type information for the EBML elements in a Mkv file or stream.

    Enum Description
    EBMLTypeInfo.TYPE
